Silent Warrior:  I'm sure LZ can handle himself.  If he has your respect... he has mine.  I did get a little mouthy.<br><br>
Sorry about the &quot;fondle&quot; bit... &quot;Cheap Shot on my part,&quot; .... got to friendlies with one stupid burst.<br><br>
I feel like a whore advocating virtue... I went the whole nine yards on Doc Spatz.  My vicious attack on Doc's person enlisted a lot of wingmen.  When I broke off target, some were confused... even disappointed.<br><br>
Hope I haven't pissed off LZ past the red line by transmitting on 7.62mm... Hope I haven't pissed off Doc... he hangs in there to take care of himself.<br><br>
I know about your fear statement... I thrived on the rushes until I couldn't push the envelope any further... I crashed and burned mentally and emotionally.  Out of the wreckage there was a little spirit that survived.<br><br>
Sounds like you have had or are having tough times... I hope that you do better than I have.<br><br>
Your depth of experience... and recognition of needed work impressed me.<br><br>
Remember to shoot low, if he's ridding a Shetland.<br><br>
Sorry LZ... Sorry Doc!<br><br>
